headline: Jacobs to Continue Leading America's Largest Community College Capital Program
summary: Jacobs (NYSE: J) has been selected by the Los Angeles Community College District (LACCD) to continue delivering program management services for its $15.1 billion BuildLACCD Bond Program, extending a relationship that has helped transform academic infrastructure across the district's nine colleges.
